ration Department, which is in charge of issuing identity cards, had the right to demand that a sharia court certify Joy's conversion. "On the question that the National Registration Department has the right to demand a certification from the Islamic court that confirms the appellant's renunciation of Islam, my answer is that NRD has the right," the judge said. "The appeal has been rejected with cause." *Your friend's e-mail address: 7 NATO soldiers killed in Afghan crash No breakthrough on resumption of six-party talks on North Korea Shimon Peres announces Israeli presidency bid Al Gore flays American citizens for Bush`s policies Yahoo! India Job Search! Get $5 USD in Free Calls! Live Cricket Ball by Ball SMS CRIC TO 7575 Express Gifts -Delivery in 24 Hrs. Post your free ad now! Persquareyard.com. Complete real estate portal. Book Classified Ads in Leading Newspapers Get instant response for your ads. Astro Predictions for You 100000+ Live ads. Post your ad. Travelling to India - Best Value Fantastic Travel deals! Plan UR trip Submit your details & save on airfares Zero Cost Money Transfers. Hurry! Get your super-saver NRI Account Yahoo! India Job Search . NRIs, One-stop shop for all your needs. Send Gifts to India Copyright &copy; Zee News Limited. All rights reserved.
